## Usage

Run this module using the `ansible` CLI (from `ansible-core`):

{% if is_api_module %}
```bash
ansible localhost -m {{ module_name }} -a "<key=value arguments>" -c local --check --diff
```

### Quick Examples

```bash
# Dry-run first (always recommended for destructive operations)
ansible localhost -m {{ module_name }} -a "{{ example_args }}" -c local --check --diff

# Apply the change
ansible localhost -m {{ module_name }} -a "{{ example_args }}" -c local --diff
```
{% else %}
```bash
ansible <host-pattern> -m {{ module_name }} -a "<key=value arguments>" -b --check --diff
```

### Quick Examples

```bash
